SPELL NAME  : Cause critical wounds
SPELL SYNTAX: -Ccw <target>
SPELL COST  : 55 SP
DESCRIPTION : The devote Cleric has the power to call upon the power of Mitra
	      to inflict damage, as well as to heal it. By force of will and
	      through the Cleric's devotion, Mitra will inflict terrible wounds
	      upon the target of her wrath.
